                     </persName>
                     
                  , doctor of physic, between the hours of seven and eight in the night, on the 28th of April last, and burglariously stealing therein, a cloth great coat, value 10 s. two silk handkerchiefs, value 2 s. his property
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>A second Count, for that he, being in the same dwelling house, and stealing the same goods and chattles, broke out of the same house, against the statute.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900526-34-person366">
