                     <interp inst="t17900526-34-verdict163" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing, but not of the burglary
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900526-34-punish164" type="punishmentDescription">
